<section class="caseStudy resources">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="caseStudyText">
                    <h2>08 Consultings Resources</h2>
                    <span></span>
                    <p>At 08 Consultings, we provide a comprehensive suite of resources designed to streamline your operations and enhance your business efficiency. Our tools and systems cover a wide range of functionalities to meet the diverse needs of our clients.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <figure><img loading="lazy" alt=""  src="~/assets/img/s_icon1.svg"></figure>
                    <h2>Online Tool for Data Tabulation</h2>
                    <p>Our online data tabulation tool allows you to quickly and easily tabulate large datasets. With user-friendly interfaces and advanced features, you can organize, summarize, and analyze your data efficiently, making it accessible for further analysis and reporting.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <figure><img loading="lazy" alt=""  src="~/assets/img/s_icon2.svg"></figure>
                    <h2>Realtime Survey Management Tool</h2>
                    <p>Manage your surveys in real-time with our survey management tool. This powerful tool enables you to design, distribute, and monitor surveys seamlessly. Track responses, analyze data on the go, and ensure your surveys are always up-to-date.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <figure><img loading="lazy" alt=""  src="~/assets/img/s_icon3.svg"></figure>
                    <h2>Realtime Panel / Respondent Management Tool</h2>
                    <p>Our panel and respondent management tool provides real-time tracking and management of your survey participants. This tool helps you manage your panel efficiently, ensuring high-quality data collection and respondent engagement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
                    <h2>Questionnaire Repositories</h2>
                    <p>Access a vast library of pre-designed questionnaires with our questionnaire repositories. These repositories provide a wide range of templates that can be customized to meet your specific research needs, saving you time and effort in survey design.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-kanban"></i>
                    <h2>HR Management System</h2>
                    <p>Optimize your human resource operations with our HR management system. This comprehensive system covers all aspects of HR management, including recruitment, employee records, performance evaluation, payroll, and benefits administration.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-archive"></i>
                    <h2>Wellness Management System</h2>
                    <p>Promote employee health and well-being with our wellness management system. This system provides tools and resources to manage wellness programs, track participation, and measure the impact of wellness initiatives on employee health and productivity.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
                    <h2>Visitor Management System</h2>
                    <p>Enhance security and streamline visitor check-ins with our visitor management system. This tool provides an efficient way to register, track, and manage visitors, ensuring a smooth and secure visitor experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-vcard"></i>
                    <h2>Inventory Management System</h2>
                    <p>Our inventory management system helps you maintain optimal inventory levels, track stock movements, and manage orders efficiently. This tool provides real-time visibility into your inventory, reducing the risk of stockouts and overstocking.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-calendar-event"></i>
                    <h2>Services Management System</h2>
                    <p>Manage your services efficiently with our services management system. This tool covers scheduling, resource allocation, service tracking, and customer relationship management, ensuring high-quality service delivery and customer satisfaction.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
                    <h2>Insurance Software System</h2>
                    <p>Our insurance software system streamlines policy management, claims processing, and customer service. This tool helps insurance providers improve operational efficiency, reduce processing times, and enhance customer experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-wallet2"></i>
                    <h2>Revenue Management System</h2>
                    <p>Maximize your revenue potential with our revenue management system. This tool provides advanced analytics and reporting features to monitor revenue streams, identify growth opportunities, and implement pricing strategies that drive profitability.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="services_box">
                    <i class="bi bi-file-earmark"></i>
                    <h2>Document Management System</h2>
                    <p>Our document management system provides a secure and organized way to store, manage, and retrieve documents. With advanced search capabilities, version control, and access permissions, this tool ensures your documents are always accessible and up-to-date.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

